Welcome to GoKos. We, as the developers of the GoKos application ("We"\), are committed to protecting your personal data and privacy. This Privacy Policy is a comprehensive guide to provide you with a clear understanding of how we handle your personal information.

To provide an optimal, personal, and relevant boarding house search service, our application requires the collection of several types of data. By using the GoKos application, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy. We encourage you to read each section carefully.

What information we collect from you, both that you provide directly and that we obtain automatically when you use the application.

1. Our purpose in using this information is to run and improve the functionality of the GoKos application.
2. With whom and under what conditions your information may be shared.
3. The steps we take to protect the security of your data.
4. The rights you have regarding your personal data.

By using the GoKos application, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy. We encourage you to read each section carefully so that you can make informed decisions and feel secure when using our services.

We collect several types of information to provide and improve our service:

a. Account Information: When you register, we collect your full name, email address, and password. If you register using Google, we will receive basic profile information from your Google account according to the permissions you grant.

b. Additional Profile Information: You have the option to complete your profile with information such as a profile photo, gender, date of birth, and emergency contact information. Providing this information is voluntary.

c. Location Information: The main feature of GoKos is to help you find the nearest boarding house. For this, with your permission, we will collect your precise geographic location data (latitude and longitude). This data is used to calculate the distance between you and the boarding house locations using the Haversine method and to display boarding houses around you.

d. Usage Information: We may collect data about how you interact with the application, such as the features you use and the time you spend, for analysis and service improvement purposes.

We use your information for several purposes:

a. Providing Core Services: To manage your account, authenticate logins, and run the main features of the application such as searching for boarding houses by location and budget.

b. Personalizing Experience: Displaying your name on the home page and providing relevant content.

c. Analysis and Improvement: Understanding how users use our application to fix bugs, develop new features, and improve the overall user experience.

d. Security: Protecting the security of your account and our platform.

We do not sell your personal information. We may share your information under the following circumstances:

a. Third-Party Service Providers: We use third-party services for application operations, such as Firebase (for database and authentication) and Google (for Google Sign-In and Google Maps). These parties only have access to the information necessary to perform their services and are obligated to protect it.

b. Legal Obligations: If required by law or a valid legal process, we may need to disclose your information.

We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.
You have the right to access and update your profile information at any time through the Edit Profile page. You can also request the deletion of your account by contacting us.

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: denih500@gmail.com.

GoKos is an application designed to help students or the general public find the nearest boarding house in the Serang campus area. This application can provide recommendations for the nearest boarding houses around the campus and your location by displaying the distance using the Haversine method. In addition, GoKos offers a GIS visualization feature for mapping boarding houses, making it easier for users who want to find a boarding house just by looking at the distribution map. With the support of GoKos, finding a boarding house becomes easier and more practical.

1. Information about boarding houses.
2. Information about distance, rental prices, and offered facilities.
3. GIS visualization to see the distribution map of boarding houses.
4. Displaying boarding houses according to your budget preferences.
5. Displaying boarding houses around you.
6. Saving boarding houses to favorites.
7. User-friendly interface.

In the main feature of the GoKos application, GIS Visualization is applied to provide digital map information on the distribution of boarding houses at a specific campus. This makes it easier to find a boarding house quickly and easily.
